Hugh Dane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_Dane 0 Hugh Dane (October 21, 1942 – May 16, 2018) was an American actor. He is best known for playing Hank the security guard on the television sitcom The Office from 2005 to 2013. Hugh_Dane ( October_21_,_1942 – May_16_,_2018 ) was an_American_actor . He is_best_known for playing Hank the_security_guard on the_television_sitcom The_Office from 2005 to 2013 .
